  "original_title": "\"\u0d95\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0ddd \u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dc1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0da0\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dda \u0dc4\u0daf\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda\":\u0d85\u0daf \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dba\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0daf\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd \u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0daf \u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dda?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"They are trying to be internationally chartered\": What happened at the Galle mouth area of \u200b\u200bstruggle this morning?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Security forces took steps early this morning (July 22) to evict the Colombo and Galle mouthpiece activists from the Presidential Secretariat and the surrounding area.",
        "The government security officers attacked many other journalists including the BBC journalists who were covering the event live.",
        "A soldier also took away the mobile phone and deleted the footage from the BBC Tamil Service's Jerin Samuel, who was at the scene.",
        "The Police Media Spokesman told the BBC that he did not know that journalists had been attacked and would look into it.",
        "Sri Lanka is becoming the center of international attention due to the many videos showing the brutal attacks by military personnel on many activists and ordinary civilians in the Colombo, Galle mouth area of \u200b\u200bstruggle."
      ],
